\id TIT - Tabo (Aramia dialect) NT - Papua New Guinea 2006 (DBL 2014) 
\h Tai 
\toc3 Tai 
\toc1 Polote Leta Taitasitamo Ododiyaęž‰ 
\toc2 Taitasi 
\mt2 POLOTE LETA  
\mt1 TAITASITAMO  
\mt2 ODODIYAęž‰  
\c 1  
\p
\v 1 Na baęž‰ Polotela, Godokono okodawala, iyo, Yaęž‰su Kelisote ebeno sose tupuimimaęž‰ hiyaęž‰hiyaęž‰ hopamo doelamiyaęž‰, baęž‰bi okopi ipuwalo na baęž‰ etala.  
\p Baęž‰ hibila, Godote yaęž‰lo tetelo pui daęž‰kaęž‰lamiholiyaęž‰, nale baęž‰bi tawakalubino hibimaęž‰ midi ipuwalo ibi kowalubilinamaęž‰ ebete na baęž‰bemaęž‰ laweniyaęž‰, iyo, ebete ubi natamo ihatiyaęž‰ nale baęž‰bi tawakalubi Godokono hibi iyaęž‰tawa komodo ba magatale, ibaęž‰te ebeno ubi komamo papamilaęž‰ha ipuwalo  
\v 2 ebeno wibohaęž‰ kaęž‰kaęž‰ lawemaęž‰ uliholo bemedenamenaęž‰. A iyaęž‰tawahala, Godoko haęž‰da amihodawahaęž‰, ebete hibi tabonomo bolamaginako, baęž‰bemaęž‰ baęž‰moe hopo tupuimihino ebete dopamo hibimaęž‰ midipaęž‰tamo kebe komo ikalamemaęž‰ dolamagiyaęž‰, ibaęž‰te baęž‰be kaęž‰kaęž‰ ebegodone hibinomolo kolawemaęž‰naęž‰.  
\v 3 Iyo, aeno Kaęž‰kaęž‰ Mulaęž‰leaęž‰medawa Godote ebeno hido tetenomolo baęž‰moe Hido Tabo hopo habanapaęž‰tamo aęž‰hawakalimiyaęž‰, baęž‰bemaęž‰ na baęž‰be tabo bolamaginakomo mabu ebete na aęž‰kiyanamiyaęž‰ nale baęž‰moe oko kowatinamaęž‰.   
\p
\v 4 O Taitasi, amaęž‰ baęž‰gala na, aeno hibimaęž‰ midi komo baęž‰ kapiyala, baęž‰bemaęž‰ amaęž‰ baęž‰be hibimaęž‰ midi ipuwalo naeno hibi gudumaęž‰ ba edaęž‰na, nale baęž‰moe leta amaęž‰tamo poememo.  
\p Baęž‰ hibila, aeno Kaęž‰kaęž‰ Mulaęž‰leaęž‰medawa baęž‰ Yaęž‰su Kelisotela, baęž‰bemaęž‰ wadiyala ebe baęž‰gala Nabiwi Godoko ibaęž‰te ibino malemale komo baęž‰gala hete komo amaęž‰tamo nikamaęž‰menaęž‰ta.   
\s1 Sose Watowatopino Emede Komo  
\p
\v 5 Numaęž‰, Kuliti hopolo naeno oko owati ipuwalo nale kebe komokomo upulaęž‰leheno daęž‰polaęž‰na, wadiyala amaęž‰ baęž‰bi komo ba ulame baęž‰be hopoeno hiyaęž‰hiyaęž‰ haboeno sose ipuwalo watowatopi nuwatiyaęž‰, nale amaęž‰ keba kaęž‰na kaęž‰kiyamitima baęž‰ba kaęž‰na. Baęž‰ hibila, amaęž‰le baęž‰be oko kowatimaęž‰ nale amaęž‰ baęž‰bolo baęž‰bemaęž‰ pimiyaęž‰puimata.  
\v 6 Baęž‰bemaęž‰ sose watodawoeno emede komo tuputupunomolo ba itana, ebeno ododili komo ipuwalo eta kapiya dehaęž‰potonomo kubate itana modobohaęž‰. Wadiyala ebete kamena kapiyagodawamaęž‰ ba edaęž‰na, ebeno gugudaęž‰te atumu tuputupunomo hibimaęž‰ midipimaęž‰ nedaęž‰hamenaęž‰, baęž‰bene tawakalubaęž‰te ibino ododili komomaęž‰ ibi talaluwapimaęž‰ baęž‰gala nabiwino tabo ulihohaęž‰pimaęž‰ kaęž‰lami modobohaęž‰.  
\v 7 Baęž‰ hibila, sose watodawate Godokono genamoeno hiyaęž‰hiyaęž‰ komo bulamena, baęž‰bemaęž‰ ebeno emede ipuwalo eta kapiya dehaęž‰potonomo kubate itana modobohaęž‰. Iyo, ebete awagaha dubumaęž‰ akedaęž‰laęž‰, baęž‰gala ebeno tepo ipuwalo koe komote tiyolo akuluhukunakalaęž‰. Baęž‰bene ebete gamoda nihohaęž‰dawamaęž‰ nedaęž‰mene, baęž‰gala ebete alaholo ipuwalo komopi kubahilame modobohaęž‰, baęž‰gala ebete haęž‰da amiho gabodo ilina dogodogodawamaęž‰ edaęž‰maęž‰ ubi ihate modobohaęž‰.  
\v 8 Wadiyala ebe huiyatiya ebeno genamalo kapela tawakalubi hidamo nowalubilinakamene, baęž‰gala ebete Godokono hido emede komo konomamo ba emalagidolona, ebe haęž‰kiya ebeno komokomo hidamo nulamenakamene. Baęž‰bene sose watodawoeno tuputupunomo emede ipuwalo wadiyala ebete ebeno ape Godokono oko kapiyamo ba ihatena kateneno kuba ubi komamo papamiwata modobohaęž‰,  
\v 9 baęž‰gala Yaęž‰sukunu dopo taęž‰matapaęž‰te ebeno hibi taboeno komokomo a keba kaęž‰na kiyaęž‰tuaęž‰menakui, wadiyala ebete baęž‰bi atu mulu komo kodakodalo naęž‰watilaęž‰motaęž‰namene. Numaęž‰, baęž‰moe gabodo hido watodawate sose tawakalubi hibi taboeno komamo ba owalubilina, puyaęž‰te baęž‰be tabago alaholohomaęž‰ dewagelena, ebete ibino daedae ukui komo baęž‰bo baęž‰hawakalilamenakomene.   
\s1 Godokono Mahilamo Haęž‰da Tabo Olamagimipino Komo  
\p
\v 10 Baęž‰bemaęž‰ Taitasi, amaęž‰ numaęž‰, Kuliti hopoeno sose tawakalubi ipuwalo komo hiliyonomate hibi taboeno komamo papamilaęž‰ha ubihaęž‰maęž‰ ba edaęž‰hana, ibaęž‰te ibino daedae ukui komamo komopi haęž‰da baęž‰bo amiholamenaka, iyo, puyaęž‰te Yunapi dubuino tama itamida kukala ko komonomomaęž‰ daęž‰gaęž‰lana, ibi baęž‰ baęž‰bako haęž‰da tabo olamagimipi ipuwalo dopopimaęž‰ edaęž‰hana.  
\v 11 Baęž‰ hibila, baęž‰baęž‰te ubi bihatena ibino haęž‰da tabo iyaęž‰tulame komodo soseno komo hiyaęž‰hiyaęž‰ badininipalaęž‰tamo ukui bilibili komo ba ikalame ibaęž‰godone koko mani kuwatelamemaęž‰, baęž‰bemaęž‰ wadiyala amaęž‰ ibi naęž‰duhilamiyaęž‰ eta kapiya tabo gaęž‰lakapomaęž‰.   
\p
\v 12 Aęž‰iye! Dopamo tetelo Kuliti hoponapaęž‰godolo eta muludawate uluhukuti ebeno tawakalubino komomaęž‰ baęž‰moe kodakoda tabo hibinomolo goiyaęž‰, â€śKuliti hoponapi hiliyonomo baęž‰ haęž‰da amihopila, iyo, ibi tumuino helohelo ilina huiyala, baęž‰bemaęž‰ ibaęž‰te hido ukui komamo aęž‰kapapamilaęž‰halaęž‰laęž‰, huiyatiya buhamamaęž‰ ba edaęž‰hana ibino kateneno ubi komo kapiya bemalagidolena!â€ť  
\v 13 Numaęž‰, baęž‰be taboeno komo baęž‰ hibinomola, baęž‰bemaęž‰ wadiyala amaęž‰ Kuliti tawakalubi konomamo naęž‰kiyahalamiyaęž‰ ibaęž‰te ibino hibimaęž‰ midi ipuwalo hidohido ukui kuwatemaęž‰.  
\v 14 Baęž‰ma kaęž‰na ibaęž‰te Yunapino komo iniwali haęž‰kiya ibino kateneno ukuiaęž‰mo daęž‰gaęž‰lanakui baęž‰bi hiyaęž‰hiyaęž‰ uwi konomamo gala akemalagidolaęž‰laęž‰, iyo, puyaęž‰te Godokono hibi komo ubihaęž‰maęž‰ dedaęž‰hui ibaęž‰te baęž‰bi dubuino hiyaęž‰hiyaęž‰ tutumu tabo gala akuliaęž‰laęž‰.   
\p
\v 15 Amaęž‰ numaęž‰, kebe lumagino tepo ipuwalo kuba dalowaęž‰ ukui kapiyate itamaęž‰naheno, baęž‰be mabumaęž‰ ebete Godoko adikumimaęž‰ dododilinako baęž‰bi hiliyonomo komate atumu dalowaęž‰haęž‰maęž‰ edaęž‰hanaka. Huiyatiya puyaęž‰te Godokono tabo hibimaęž‰ midihino, baęž‰gala puyaęž‰te ibino tepo ipuwalo kuba dalowaęž‰ ukui demalagidolena, ibaęž‰te Godoko adikumimaęž‰ eta hido komo ododi modobohaęž‰, mabu ebete ibaęž‰tamo dopamo dikalamiyaęž‰ baęž‰be hido mulu tepo ipuwa baęž‰gala emalagidolo komo ibaęž‰te yaęž‰lo aęž‰kubahilamiyaęž‰.  
\v 16 Baęž‰be mabumaęž‰ ibi haęž‰kiya ibi Godokono hibi komo iyaęž‰tawahapimaęž‰ gaęž‰lanaka, huiyatiya ibino kuba ododili komate baęž‰moe komo behawakalimina, ibaęž‰te ebeno komo hibilo kiyaęž‰tawahanahaęž‰. Iyo, ibino emede komate kuba dalowaęž‰maęž‰ ba edaęž‰hana Godotamo kapapamilaęž‰hanahaęž‰, baęž‰bemaęž‰ ebeno umi ipuwalo ibi modobohaęž‰ ebetamo eta hido komo ododimaęž‰.   
\c 2  
\s1 Sose Tawakalubino Hiyaęž‰hiyaęž‰ Komomaęž‰ Polote Komo Tutumu Tabo Dolamagiyaęž‰  
\p
\v 1 Naeno gudu Taitasi, amaęž‰ huiyatiya tawakalubi hidamo niyaęž‰tulamenakuyaęž‰, Yaęž‰sukunu dopo taęž‰matapaęž‰te ebeno mulu taboeno komokomo a keba kaęž‰na kiyaęž‰tuaęž‰menakui baęž‰ba kaęž‰na.  
\v 2 Baęž‰bemaęž‰ puyaęž‰te hibimaęž‰ midipi ipuwalo nabimaęž‰ dedaęž‰hana, wadiyala amaęž‰ ibi naęž‰kiyalamiyaęž‰, ibaęž‰te hidohido mulu ukui uwatelo ibi haęž‰kiya ibino komo hidamo ba ulamena, ibino emede komate komopino umi ipuwalo hidonomomaęž‰ nedaęž‰hamenaęž‰. Iyo, na ubila ibaęž‰te ibino hibimaęž‰ midi ipuwalo baęž‰gala ibino malemale hawakalimi ipuwalo baęž‰gala ibi Yaęž‰suku mabumaęž‰ duwatenaka, baęž‰bi temeteme ipuwalo ibaęž‰te kodakodalo naęž‰laęž‰motaęž‰hanamenaęž‰.   
\p
\v 3 Amaęž‰ baęž‰ atumu hibimaęž‰ midipi menokobi naęž‰kakiyalamiyaęž‰, ibaęž‰te Godokono holoholo hapulu hidonomamo ba emedena ebe mabumaęž‰ talonapimaęž‰ nedaęž‰hanamenaęž‰. Baęž‰ma kaęž‰na ibaęž‰te helo galaęž‰ipi gao beya konomamo niho modobohaęž‰ ibino ukui komate daedaemaęž‰ edaęž‰hakapomaęž‰, baęž‰gala ibaęž‰te haęž‰da tabo olamagimi komodo komopi akakubahilamaęž‰laęž‰. Wadiyala ibaęž‰te huiyatiya uli ape kamenakamena hidamo ba iyaęž‰tulame  
\v 4 ibaęž‰tamo mulu ukui baęž‰bo nikalamenakamenaęž‰, ibaęž‰te ibino awi baęž‰gala gugudi malemalelo kemalagidolenamaęž‰.  
\v 5 Iyo, uli ape kamenakamenate ibi haęž‰kiya ibino komokomo ba ulamena ibino tepo ipuwalo eta dalowaęž‰ ukui komote itana modobohaęž‰, baęž‰gala ibaęž‰te ibino genama gulu hiyaęž‰hiyaęž‰ oko hidamo ba owatihona ibino awino ubi komamo baęž‰papamilaęž‰hanakomenaęž‰. Baęž‰ hibila, kamenakamenate baęž‰ba kaęž‰na demedenamenaęž‰, eta hibimaęž‰ midihaęž‰ dawate ibino komomaęž‰ Godokono tabo kubamaęž‰ goe gabo aęž‰kumaęž‰mene.   
\p
\v 6 Wadiyala amaęž‰ baęž‰ atumu uli ape dubu naęž‰kakiyalamiyaęž‰, ibaęž‰te ibi haęž‰kiya ibino komokomo hidamo nulamenakamenaęž‰.  
\v 7 Baęž‰gala naeno gudu, wadiyala amaęž‰ amiaęž‰no hiliyonomo ododili komo ipuwalo hido go baęž‰bi uli ape dubatamo naęž‰hawakaliminakuyaęž‰ ibaęž‰te amaęž‰ hidamo kibamitinamaęž‰. Baęž‰ma kaęž‰na Godokono tabo iyaęž‰tulame okoeno komomaęž‰ maęž‰lapila netewa komote amaęž‰godolo itanaheno, wadiyala amaęž‰le amiaęž‰no tabo ulihopino komokomo ba emalagidolena amaęž‰ tuputupunomolo nemedeniyaęž‰.  
\v 8 Iyo, amaęž‰le tawakalubi hidonomo tabamo nowalubilinakuyaęž‰, baęž‰bene eta lumagiti aęž‰kamodobamene amiaęž‰no iyaęž‰tulame komo kubamaęž‰ goe. Baęž‰ baęž‰ma kaęž‰na puyaęž‰te amaęž‰go dalaholohona, ibaęž‰te a hibimaęž‰ midipino komomaęž‰ eta kuba tabo gaęž‰la gabo nipo dohowadiminaęž‰ baęž‰bo kohilopohomaęž‰naęž‰.   
\p
\v 9 Baęž‰gala koko okopi dubate pui manaęž‰mo duwatiyaęž‰ ibino huiyahaęž‰ oko kowatihonamaęž‰, baęž‰bi huiyahaęž‰ okopi ipuwalo puyaęž‰te hibimaęž‰ midipimaęž‰ dedaęž‰hana, wadiyala amaęž‰ ibi naęž‰kiyalamiyaęž‰ ibaęž‰te ibino hiliyonomo oko ipuwalo ibino namutulubi kokalakaluilamenamaęž‰ ibaęž‰te ibino ubi komamo naęž‰papamilaęž‰hanakamenaęž‰. Iyo, ibino namutulubaęž‰te hiyaęž‰hiyaęž‰ oko ibaęž‰tamo ba ikalame, modobohaęž‰ ibaęž‰te baęž‰bi oko mabumaęž‰ ibaęž‰tamo kuba tabo gaęž‰la,  
\v 10 baęž‰gala ibaęž‰te ibino namutulubino mani pilolo uwateheno, wadiyala ibi huiyatiya ibino tuputupu ododili komamo baęž‰moe komo naęž‰hawakaliminakamenaęž‰, ibino hiliyonomo oko owatiho komo ipuwalo eta haęž‰da ododi komo kapiyate kitanahaęž‰. Baęž‰bemaęž‰ ibaęž‰te baęž‰ baęž‰ba kaęž‰na aeno Kaęž‰kaęž‰ Mulaęž‰leaęž‰medawa Godokono iyaęž‰tulame komokomo hidamo ba hawakalilamena, tawakalubi hiliyonomate baęž‰bi komo hidohidonomomaęž‰ baęž‰gaęž‰lanakomenaęž‰.   
\p
\v 11 Baęž‰ hibila, Godote ebeno malemale komo baęž‰ma kaęž‰na hawakalimiyaęž‰, ebete hopo habanapi hiliyonomoeno kaęž‰kaęž‰ komulaęž‰lelamemaęž‰ atamo baęž‰bemaęž‰ piyaęž‰.  
\v 12 Baęž‰bemaęž‰ ebeno malemale komote a biyaęž‰tuaęž‰mena, ale kuba ododili ipuwane baęž‰gala baęž‰moe hopoeno kateneno ubi komone ohobilaęž‰hate, a haęž‰kiya aeno komo hidamo ba ulamena Godokono tuputupu emede komamo ebe kapiyatamo baęž‰papamilaęž‰halenakomaęž‰.  
\v 13 Baęž‰ baęž‰ba kaęž‰na aeno Kaęž‰kaęž‰ Mulaęž‰leaęž‰medawa Yaęž‰su Kelisokono Hidonomo Hegelate uluhukumaęž‰ ale uliholo bemedenamaęž‰, mabu baęž‰ba tetelo ebete ebeno alo konomago atamo hibilo kopemaęž‰ne, iyo, ebe baęž‰ aeno Kodawa Godotela.  
\v 14 Baęž‰ hibila, ebete ebeno kaęž‰kaęž‰ gobogobamo a mabumaęž‰ baęž‰ma kaęž‰na ihatiyaęž‰, ebete a aeno hiliyonomo kuba ododili ipuwane baęž‰gala aeno tepo ipuwoeno dalowaęž‰ ukui komone a uluhukuaęž‰tete, ale ebeno tawakalubinomomaęž‰ ba edaęž‰hana aeno ubi konomo baęž‰bo bihatenamaęž‰ hido komokomo kapiya kododilinamaęž‰.   
\p
\v 15 Baęž‰bemaęž‰ naeno gudu, Godote kebe helo konomo amaęž‰tamo dikamiyaęž‰la, wadiyala amaęž‰le toleheno baęž‰be heloamo baęž‰moi komokomo hidamo ba iyaęž‰tulame, tabo ulihopi ipuwalo hidohidopino ukui kodakoduilamete huiyatiya kuba ododilipi dito naęž‰kiyahalamenakuyaęž‰. Iyo, amiaęž‰no hiliyonomo ododili ipuwalo sose tawakalubaęž‰tamo gigiho akaęž‰hiyaęž‰midalaęž‰, ibi ipuwalo etate tabo baęž‰ma kaęž‰na akagaaęž‰laęž‰ amaęž‰ sose watodawahaęž‰.   
\c 3  
\s1 Hibimaęž‰ Midipino Tuputupu Emede Komo  
\p
\v 1 Baęž‰bemaęž‰ Taitasi, ale Kuliti hopoeno sose tawakalubi dopamo kebe komo kiyaęž‰tulamimaęž‰, wadiyala amaęž‰ baęž‰be atu komo ibi gala baęž‰ma kaęž‰na naęž‰kakiyalamiyaęž‰, ibaęž‰te gabomanino hiyaęž‰hiyaęž‰ okopino tabamo naęž‰papamilaęž‰hanakamenaęž‰. Baęž‰gala wadiyala ibaęž‰te naęž‰hidonakamenaęž‰ hiliyonomo hidohido komo kododilimaęž‰,  
\v 2 baęž‰bene ibaęž‰te eta lumagino komomaęž‰ kuba tabo akagaęž‰lalaęž‰, baęž‰gala komopaęž‰go olowabeletihuihino tatabapimaęž‰ ba edaęž‰hana, baęž‰be tataba emede komo ibaęž‰te tawakalubi hiliyonomatamo naęž‰hawakaliminakamenaęž‰.   
\s1 Aeno Kaęž‰kaęž‰ Mulaęž‰leaęž‰me Komo  
\p
\v 3 Baęž‰ hibila, ale dopamo daedae ukui ipuwalo ba emedena, Godotamo papamilaęž‰haheno hibo gabo dito ududiyaęž‰maęž‰. Numaęž‰, baęž‰ba tetelo a haęž‰kiya a kokalakaluiaęž‰memaęž‰ ale aeno kateneno hiyaęž‰hiyaęž‰ ubi komamo papamilaęž‰hanakuimaęž‰, baęž‰bene aeno emede ipuwalo hiyaęž‰hiyaęž‰ kuba ododili komate ba tabotabohona, ale komopino dogodogo ilina mabumaęž‰ ibaęž‰tamo baęž‰bo maubahanakuimaęž‰, iyo, komopino maubaha ipuwalo ibaęž‰te ago alaholohomaęž‰ ba ewagelena ale baęž‰ atumu ibaęž‰go alaholohomaęž‰ kewagelenamimaęž‰.  
\v 4 Huiyatiya kalakala konomola, aeno Kaęž‰kaęž‰ Mulaęž‰leaęž‰medawa baęž‰ Godotela, iyo, ale aeno modobohaęž‰ komokomo ipuwalo ba emedena ebeno hido owalubi komote ebeno malemale emalagidolo komago atamo hibilo uluhukuyaęž‰.  
\v 5 Baęž‰bemaęž‰ a haęž‰kiya aeno heloamo kebe kapiyakapiya hidohido komo dododilinakuimaęž‰, ebete baęž‰bi ododili komamo a kowalubiyaęž‰haęž‰, ao, ebete huiyatiya ebegodolo ditana baęž‰be malemale komo kapiyanomamo aeno kaęž‰kaęž‰ aęž‰mulaęž‰leaęž‰miyaęž‰. Numaęž‰, ebeno Gobogobote aeno tepo ipuwoeno dalowaęž‰ ukulaleaęž‰me helo atamo ikaaęž‰miyaęž‰ ale ebeno uli kaęž‰kaęž‰mo kohawakalahalemaęž‰, baęž‰bemaęž‰ Godote baęž‰be gabodo ebeno kaęž‰kaęž‰ mulaęž‰ komo atamo dito ikaaęž‰miyaęž‰.  
\v 6 Iyo, ebete aeno Kaęž‰kaęž‰ Mulaęž‰leaęž‰medawa Yaęž‰su Kelisoko ipuwado ebeno Gobogoboeno helo konomo aeno tepo ipuwamo aęž‰haminuyaęž‰,  
\v 7 mabu ebete ebeno ubi baęž‰ma kaęž‰na ihatiyaęž‰, ebete ebeno malemale komodo a tuputupupimaęž‰ miditi, baęž‰bene ale ebegodone lawemaęž‰ uliholo daęž‰latiminamaęž‰ baęž‰be wibohaęž‰ kaęž‰kaęž‰te atamo hibinomolo kuluhukumaęž‰ne.  
\v 8 Amaęž‰ numaęž‰, baęž‰moe iyaęž‰tulame tabo komo baęž‰ hibinomola.  
\s1 Polote Taitasikono Oko Owati Komomaęž‰ Tabo Dolamagiyaęž‰  
\p Naeno gudu, na ubila puyaęž‰te ibino hibimaęž‰ midi komo Godotamo daęž‰miyaęž‰ti, amaęž‰le ibi baęž‰moi hiyaęž‰hiyaęž‰ komo hidonomamo niyaęž‰tulamiyaęž‰, baęž‰bene ibaęž‰te ibino ubi konomamo nihatenakamenaęž‰ komo tawakalubi kowalubilimaęž‰ ibaęž‰te ibino emede ipuwane hidohido komo kuluhukulatelemaęž‰, iyo, baęž‰be gabodo komo hiliyonomo tawakalubaęž‰te naeno iyaęž‰tulame komone hido owalubi komokomo kuwatemaęž‰naęž‰.  
\v 9 Huiyatiya wadiyala amaęž‰ tawakalubino daedae olowabeletihui komone dito nohobiguyaęž‰, baęž‰ baęž‰ma kaęž‰na Yunapi iniwalino mahilo iyaęž‰tulame komomaęž‰, baęž‰gala Godote Moseseko ipuwado tawakalubaęž‰tamo dikalamiyaęž‰, amaęž‰le baęž‰bi hiyaęž‰hiyaęž‰ Tutumu Taboeno ugumuili ipuwa komomaęž‰ anagiyaęž‰mida ukui tawakalubaęž‰tamo ikalameheno ibaęž‰go akolowabeletihuiaęž‰laęž‰. Baęž‰ hibila, baęž‰bakobako tabo gaęž‰la ipuwane eta hido owalubi komote aęž‰kuluhukale!  
\v 10 Baęž‰bemaęž‰ hibimaęž‰ midipi ipuwalo eta dubuti olowabeletihui komamo ibi anagiyaęž‰midalemaęž‰ dewagelenako, wadiyala amaęž‰le ebe kapiya o netewa tetaęž‰mo koamo naęž‰kiyahamiyaęž‰ ebete baęž‰be komo komiyaęž‰pamaęž‰. Ebete huiyatiya amiaęž‰no tabo ulihino atu kuba ododi daęž‰katupuimimini, baęž‰ba tetelo sose tawakalubaęž‰te ebetamo talona nihataęž‰menaęž‰ ebete ibino kapiyuimi komamo gala akapaęž‰laęž‰.  
\v 11 Baęž‰ hibila, baęž‰bako dubuino ododi komone amaęž‰ kiyaęž‰tawamaęž‰naęž‰ta, ebete ebeno tepo ipuwalo Godokono hibi komone yaęž‰lo ohobigui, iyo, ebe haęž‰kiya ebeno kuba ododili komodo baęž‰moe komo behawakalimina, ebete kuba huiya hibinomolo kolawemaęž‰ne.   
\s1 Polote Leta Kuititi Hapulu Tabo Komokomo Dolamagiyaęž‰  
\p
\v 12 Baęž‰bemaęž‰ Taitasi, amaęž‰ numaęž‰, tete tatalila na Polote Atimasiko o Tikikasiko ibi ipuwalo eta kapiya amaęž‰tamo kopoememaęž‰nemo, baęž‰bene ebete amaęž‰tamo hawela ikamaęž‰tepamaęž‰ daęž‰pemene, wadiyala amaęž‰ na unamemaęž‰ Nikapolasi habamo pe gabo tiyonomolo naęž‰hiduimiyaęž‰, mabu nale nopo baęž‰ma kaęž‰na ihatimo hopoeno giba teteno kuititi tetaęž‰mo baęž‰moe habalo kemedemaęž‰.  
\v 13 Baęž‰bene Apolosiko baęž‰gala gabomanino tutumu iyaęž‰tawadawa Sinasiko ibi netewapaęž‰te natamo atumu kakapuluhukumaęž‰, wadiyala amaęž‰ ibi hidamo nowalubiliyaęž‰, iyo, ibino pe gabomaęž‰ kebe modobohaęž‰ komate daęž‰polaęž‰lamaęž‰na baęž‰bi komo amaęž‰ malemalelo dito naęž‰tuputupuilamiyaęž‰.   
\p
\v 14 Baęž‰gala eta komo. Aeno hibimaęž‰ midipaęž‰te Kuliti hopolo demedehona, wadiyala amaęž‰ ibi naęž‰tutumulateliyaęž‰, ibaęž‰te ibino emede ipuwalo hegehege mani oko ba owatiho ibi haęž‰kiya ibino modobohaęž‰ komokomo nulamenakamenaęž‰, baęž‰bene komo tetelo ibaęž‰te hiyaęž‰hiyaęž‰ gabo atumu kakulamemaęž‰naęž‰ hidohido komo komopaęž‰tamo kododilimaęž‰. Iyo, wadiyala ibaęž‰te ibino ukui konomamo nihatenakamenaęž‰ baęž‰ba kaęž‰na kewagelenamaęž‰, ibaęž‰te ibino emede ipuwalo buhamamaęž‰ edaęž‰hakapomaęž‰.   
\p
\v 15 Baęž‰bemaęž‰ puyaęž‰te nagodolo demedena, ibi hiliyonomate ibino nolata tabo amaęž‰tamo poemaęž‰, baęž‰bene Kuliti hopolo puyaęž‰te Godoko hibimaęž‰ midi ipuwalo a demalagidoloena, wadiyala amaęž‰ aeno nolata tabo ibaęž‰tamo nolamagiyaęž‰.  
\p Wadiyala Godokono malemale komote laęž‰ hiliyonomagodolo nitanamene. Baęž‰moe baęž‰ naeno tabo kuititila. Baęž‰baęž‰la.   